===Etymology 2===
Alternative form of [[hjem]]. Likely caused by influence from {{der|en|non|heim||home, homewards}}, the accusative form of {{m|non|heimr||abode, world, land}}, from {{der|en|gem-pro|*haimaz}}. More at [[home]].
